\fs36 \cf0 \cb2 \outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec3 We at Regen Studio believe that theatre can have a profound impact on learning. That is why we are excited to introduce the concept of 
\f1\i Innovation Theatre
\f0\i0 , a collaborative project with {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.instagram.com/expressareser/"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 \strokec4 Expressar & Ser}}, a company providing theatre classes for children, adults and corporates in the city of S\'e3o Paulo. \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

