\fs44 \cf0 \cb2 \strokec3 Smart City Innovation Process: The Hague\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs32 \cf0 \cb2 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 Regen Studio has developed the innovation process used by the Expertise Centre for Digital Innovation and Smart Cities at the City of The Hague. It is an adaptation of Design Thinking, specifically tuned for the complex environment of city governments. The process is a comprehensive and flexible protocol that the Innovation Consultants of the City are applying in more than 15 projects, such as in the award-winning Living Lab Scheveningen. It guides them through the innovation phases of Problem Definition, Ideation, Prototyping, Validation and Experiment, by co-creation and consensus-making.\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

